OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early low cloud clearing to
OL,6,Fleave a very warm day with spells of
OL,7,Fsunshine. A band of cloud and some
OL,8,Fshowers however will move eastwards
OL,9,Fthroughout the day with a few heavier
OL,10,Fand thundery showers developing later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers clearing to the east
OL,13,Fthis evening leaving many dry with
OL,14,Fclear spells. Some rain or showers
OL,15,Fwill continue across northern Scotland
OL,16,Fand returning later in the southwest.
OL,17,FMild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
